{
  "text": "The following model was employed for the analysis: Vol. 9, No. 6; The Ordinary Least Square (OLS) regression is run on SPSS version 19. The model is derived on the basis of previous studies such as [CITATION_1] and [CITATION_2] . Independent Variable (IV) or explanatory variable that has been identified include age, size, tangibility, liquidity, profitability, growth, investment and taxation.",
  "correct_citation": {
    "[CITATION_1]": "153728300",
    "[CITATION_2]": "155940037"
